Chip shop boss John Clarkson has created a new answer to the Creme Egg question of ` how do you eat yours ' .
Eschewing the savoury favourites of sausage and egg or mince pies .
Mr Clarkson decided to wrap the Easter delicacies in pastry before they were battered and deep-fried .
The pie is his very own ` Pie-egg-ra ' dish - a hit with customers .